## Send a WhatsApp (WA) template message
Occurs after a user submitted a new Google form. If the user opted-in for WA notifications during the form submission, a template message will be sent via WhatsApp.

**IMPORTANT!**
1. You will need to create a new WA template message on the [Meta Business portal]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}
2. To send outgoing WA messages you'll need an Access Token and a WhatsApp Business Account ID. These can be obtained via Meta Developers Portal after creating an a new App. Please refer to this [n8n blog article on creating WhatsApp bots]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}
